1.0.name: wordpress/woocommerce-custom-currencies
1.0.description: A WordPress and WooCommerce plugin/extension that allows users to add their own currencies or to edit an existing currency’s symbol or label. You can also define conversion rates for your custom currency (if it is not supported by PayPal) to use PayPal gateway through another supported currency like USD or GBP.
